Trade/Device Name(s): Bioland G-425-2V Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Bioland G-425-2 Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Bioland G-425-2V and G-425-2 blood glucose monitoring systems for home use in diabetes monitoring without Bluetooth connectivity
Indications for Use Summary: Quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from fingertip; self-testing by people with diabetes at home to monitor effectiveness of diabetes control; not for diagnosis, screening, or use in neonates
